<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:202'>　周易章句證異卷三</span>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='202:222'>　　　　　　　　　　内閣中書翟均廉撰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='222:227'>彖上傳</span>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='227:260'>　鄭𤣥合彖傳於經置爻詞後大象前<span class='krp-note'>本淳于後吴仁/傑語廉案石介</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='260:293'>　<span class='krp-note'>稱孔子作彖傳於六/爻之前説與此異</span>王弼自坤以下彖傳置卦詞後</span>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='293:334'>　大象前<span class='krp-note'>陸德明孔穎達李鼎祚蘇軾張子從之世王/宋子夏傳朱震李衡張浚鄭汝諧項安</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='334:382'>　<span class='krp-note'>宗傳趙彦肅王申子李簡董楷同置周燔彖傳置卦/詞後爻詞前文低一字  趙汝楳  卦詞後爻詞前</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='382:408'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-1b' );" name="003-1b" class="pb">[003-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='408:456'>　<span class='krp-note'>乾坤二卦置文言前釋李過方逢辰置卦詞後大象/前乾坤二卦置文言  彖處前  董真卿以彖傳置</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='456:496'>　<span class='krp-note'>大象後/小象前</span>胡旦復出彖傳亦為一篇<span class='krp-note'>次一第邵子晁説/之次  二以卦爻</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='496:535'>　<span class='krp-note'>為第文低一字一/吴仁傑作彖傳</span>胡瑗分上彖下彖為二篇<span class='krp-note'>上彖次/一  吕</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='535:584'>　<span class='krp-note'>大防連二經上彖次三文低一字從程逈作彖上一/  吕祖謙作彖上傳次第一朱子  之  税與權吴</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='584:622'>　<span class='krp-note'>澄胡炳文胡一桂熊良輔梁/寅諸儒同  俞琰彖傳上一</span>王洙以彖傳為彖詞次</span>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='622:664'>　第二<span class='krp-note'>廉案洙惟以爻詞為經卦詞别為一篇次/第一葉適為即藝文志所謂古易十二篇</span>鄭厚</span>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='664:678'>　無彖傳<span class='krp-note'>云後人/所作</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='678:691'>大哉乾元萬物資始乃統天</span>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='691:717'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-2a' );" name="003-2a" class="pb">[003-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='717:741'>　鄭𤣥以下附彖傳於經者加彖曰字　馮椅商飛卿</span>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='741:762'>　改為賛曰趙汝楳无彖曰字<span class='krp-note'>直接/卦詞</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='762:772'>雲行雨施品物流形</span>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='772:789'>大明終始六位時成時乗六龍以御天</span>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='789:819'>　吳澄以大明終始三句移萬國咸寧之後<span class='krp-note'>謂首出二/句言聖人</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='819:858'>　<span class='krp-note'>之元亨大明三句言聖人之利貞舊/本錯簡在品物流形之下今正之</span>徐在漢曰古文</span>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='858:889'>　大明終始節在乃利貞後首出庶物前<span class='krp-note'>陸時位云此/照古本漢後</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='889:924'>　<span class='krp-note'>儒將大明節挿入乾道節前以贋亂/真  毛竒齡曰偽古本乃利貞後謬</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='924:950'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-2b' );" name="003-2b" class="pb">[003-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='950:967'>乾道變化各正性命保合太和乃利貞</span>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='967:977'>首出庶物萬國咸寧</span>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='977:991'>至哉坤元萬物資生乃順承天</span>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='991:1010'>坤厚載物徳合无疆含𢎞光大品物咸亨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1010:1028'>牝馬地類行地无疆柔順利貞君子攸行</span>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1028:1051'>先迷失道後順得常西南得朋乃與類行東北喪朋乃</span>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1051:1056'>終有慶</span>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1056:1066'>安貞之吉應地无疆</span>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1066:1092'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-3a' );" name="003-3a" class="pb">[003-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1092:1102'>屯剛柔始交而難生</span>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1102:1111'>動乎險中大亨貞</span>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1111:1139'>　險毛竒齡云漢劉修碑作儉<span class='krp-note'>字形/之通</span>　陸時位以大亨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1139:1172'>　貞雷雨之動滿盈為一節<span class='krp-note'>云先儒以大亨係上動/乎險中不可為大亨</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1172:1190'>雷雨之動滿盈天造草昧宜建侯而不寧</span>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1190:1219'>　盈荀爽虞翻李鼎祚作形<span class='krp-note'>廉案今李/本作盈</span>　陸時位以天</span>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1219:1255'>　造草昩為一節<span class='krp-note'>云先儒以雷雨之動句/属利建侯大是可商</span>　而鄭𤣥讀曰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1255:1296'>　能能猶安也<span class='krp-note'>廉案孔穎逹禮運疏云古之能字皆作/耐字音來能字乃假借鼈三足為能後</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1296:1322'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-3b' );" name="003-3b" class="pb">[003-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1322:1368'>　<span class='krp-note'>世傳書世異耐字悉作能字惟耐以天下為一家及/人不耐無樂仍耐字亦有誤不安寸直作而者則易</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1368:1412'>　<span class='krp-note'>屯彖云利建侯而不寧是也據此則耐不寧孔氏/亦作能不寧解不知周易正義何以仍作而字解</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1412:1423'>蒙山下有險險而止蒙</span>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1423:1443'>　明晋府古本止上有能字<span class='krp-note'>張元/冲傳</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1443:1466'>蒙亨以亨行時中也匪我求童蒙童蒙求我志應也初</span>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1466:1488'>筮告以剛中也再三瀆瀆則不告瀆蒙也蒙以養正</span>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1488:1493'>聖功也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1493:1528'>　明晋府本無以亨二字<span class='krp-note'>張冲元傳二俞琰曰/或云亨行  字羡文</span>　陸徳</span>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1528:1554'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-4a' );" name="003-4a" class="pb">[003-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1554:1587'>　明曰一作童蒙來求我<span class='krp-note'>晁說之曰非亷按陸徳/明所云疑是王注中語</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1587:1607'>需須也險在前也剛健而不陷其義不困窮矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1607:1630'>需有孚光亨貞吉位乎天位以正中也利渉大川徃有</span>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1630:1634'>功也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1634:1657'>　位乎之位鄭𤣥讀曰涖　毛竒齡曰石經作位于</span>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1657:1668'>訟上剛下險險而健訟</span>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1668:1691'>　朱子曰訟上剛下險屬上句險而健訟屬下句俞琰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1691:1707'>　曰健字句絶或以健訟相連誤矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1707:1733'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-4b' );" name="003-4b" class="pb">[003-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1733:1756'>訟有孚窒惕中吉剛來而得中也終凶訟不可成也利</span>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1756:1774'>見大人尚正中也不利渉大川入于淵也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1774:1790'>師衆也貞正也能以衆正可以王矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1790:1813'>剛中而應行險而順以此毒天下而民從之吉又何咎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1813:1816'>矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1816:1821'>比吉也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1821:1858'>　郭京曰比吉下誤增也字<span class='krp-note'>凡彖傳先舉彖詞後以義/結彖辭無也字  王昭素</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1858:1893'>　<span class='krp-note'>曰多也字項/安世從之</span>朱子本義曰比吉也三字疑衍文<span class='krp-note'>胡炳/文從</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1893:1919'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-5a' );" name="003-5a" class="pb">[003-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1919:1958'>　<span class='krp-note'>梁寅恭義/不從本義</span>又語録曰也字羡<span class='krp-note'>熊良輔從之毛竒/齡曰朱子非是</span>陳仁</span>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1958:1981'>　錫本删比吉也三字謹案　周易述義有比吉也三</span>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1981:2021'>　字<span class='krp-note'>王弼孔穎逹張子程子蘓軾楊時朱/震楊萬里張浚李衡諸儒俱有也字</span>按釋文引子</span>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2021:2044'>　夏傳云地得水而柔水得地而流故曰比三句今宋</span>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2044:2054'>　本無此不知何屬</span>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2054:2063'>比輔也下順從也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2063:2086'>原筮元永貞无咎以剛中也不寧方來上下應也後夫</span>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2086:2093'>凶其道窮也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2093:2119'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-5b' );" name="003-5b" class="pb">[003-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2119:2134'>小畜柔得位而上下應之曰小畜</span>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2134:2146'>健而巽剛中而志行乃亨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2146:2163'>宻雲不雨尚徃也自我西郊施未行也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2163:2170'>履柔履剛也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2170:2186'>説而應乎乾是以履虎尾不咥人亨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2186:2200'>剛中正履帝位而不疚光明也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2200:2230'>　疚陸績作疾<span class='krp-note'>毛竒齡曰/疚疾形誤</span>陸時位曰此節係文言危者</span>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2230:2251'>　安其位章後人附入於此<span class='krp-note'>云古本/可證</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2251:2277'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-6a' );" name="003-6a" class="pb">[003-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2277:2300'>泰小徃大來吉亨則是天地交而萬物通也上下交而</span>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2300:2323'>其志同也内陽而外隂内健而外順内君子而外小人</span>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2323:2334'>君子道長小人道消也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2334:2357'>否之匪人不利君子貞大徃小來則是天地不交而萬</span>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2357:2380'>物不通也上下不交而天下無邦也内隂而外陽内柔</span>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2380:2401'>而外剛内小人而外君子小人道長君子道消也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2401:2434'>　吴澄作否不利君子貞三字<span class='krp-note'>去之匪人三字舊本/因經文衍而誤增也</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2434:2450'>同人柔得位得中而應乎乾曰同人</span>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2450:2476'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-6b' );" name="003-6b" class="pb">[003-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2476:2481'>同人曰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2481:2518'>　王昭素同人曰三字錯<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰虞翻軰諸儒无一/人為之説者特王弼失之耳</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2518:2560'>　胡瑗云三字衍<span class='krp-note'>程子朱子從之張胡一桂熊良輔董/楷胡炳文同    慎甫曰同人曰三</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2560:2597'>　<span class='krp-note'>字非衍同/查慎行</span>　吴澄删同人曰三字<span class='krp-note'>朱升陳仁錫同/毛竒齡曰大繆</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2597:2637'>　<span class='krp-note'>案王弼非二所能乾之所行故特曰同人曰/孔穎逹曰猶言同人卦曰也趙汝楳諸儒同</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2637:2659'>同人于野亨利涉大川乾行也文明以健中正而應</span>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2659:2675'>君子正也唯君子為能通天下之志</span>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2675:2693'>大有柔得尊位大中而上下應之曰大有</span>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2693:2719'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-7a' );" name="003-7a" class="pb">[003-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2719:2738'>其徳剛健而文明應乎天而時行是以元亨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2738:2755'>謙亨天道下濟而光明地道卑而上行</span>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2755:2778'>天道虧盈而益謙地道變盈而流謙鬼神害盈而福謙</span>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2778:2801'>人道惡盈而好謙謙尊而光卑而不可喻君子之終也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2801:2815'>　虧馬融作毁　福亰房作富</span>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2815:2827'>豫剛應而志行順以動豫</span>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2827:2845'>豫順以動故天地如之而况建侯行師乎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2845:2868'>天地以順動故日月不過而四時不忒聖人以順動則</span>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2868:2894'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-7b' );" name="003-7b" class="pb">[003-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2894:2909'>刑罰清而民服豫之時義大矣哉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2909:2930'>　忒京房作貸　惠棟作貣<span class='krp-note'>云貣與/貸通</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2930:2942'>隨剛來而下柔動而説随</span>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2942:2954'>大亨貞无咎而天下随時</span>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2954:2991'>　荀爽作大亨利貞<span class='krp-note'>陸徳明曰正義作大亨利貞/  郭京曰大亨下脫利字</span>虞翻</span>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2991:3029'>　蜀才王弼作隨時<span class='krp-note'>陸德明孔穎逹李鼎祚劉牧王大/安石蘓軾程子郭忠孝郭雍吕</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='3029:3076'>　<span class='krp-note'>臨楊時楊萬里朱震李衡王宗傳張浚趙彦肅鄭汝/諧王逢吕祖謙趙汝楳蔡淵從之  李簡梁寅陳仁</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='3076:3123'>　<span class='krp-note'>錫鄭申甫陸敬臻陸時位張振淵徐在漢洪原毛竒/齡同  查慎行曰本義從王肅本大象注亦云随時</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='3123:3149'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-8a' );" name="003-8a" class="pb">[003-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='3149:3192'>　<span class='krp-note'>休息此處/似不當改</span>王肅陸績作隨之<span class='krp-note'>胡旦曰篆字之為□時/為旹轉𨽻者増日為時</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='3192:3240'>　<span class='krp-note'>朱王昭素曰舊本無此而字有之字晁説之從其説/  子本義亦從王肅  邱富國胡炳文吳澄胡一桂</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='3240:3287'>　<span class='krp-note'>俞琰林希元洪守美洪啟初同倒項安世曰此則上/時字為聲之誤下時字為字之  也或曰古時字從</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3287:3314'>　<span class='krp-note'>之故之時二字易雜/然則皆字之誤也</span>惠棟改作随之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3314:3323'>隨時之義大矣哉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3323:3365'>　諸説見上<span class='krp-note'>趙汝楳曰先儒或改作隨之時義他卦云/時義者指其時與義則時義為两事也今</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3365:3412'>　<span class='krp-note'>云隨時之義謂所隨者時其義甚大則時義為一事/聖人變文以明理勿改可也  俞琰曰時之當作之</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3412:3442'>　<span class='krp-note'>時豫遯姤旅四卦例則之時倒/為時之盖由上文之誤而誤也</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3442:3468'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-8b' );" name="003-8b" class="pb">[003-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3468:3480'>蠱剛上而柔下巽而止蠱</span>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3480:3503'>蠱元亨而天下治也利渉大川徃有事也先甲三日後</span>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3503:3515'>甲三日終則有始天行也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3515:3522'>臨剛浸而長</span>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3522:3531'>説而順剛中而應</span>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3531:3541'>大亨以正天之道也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3541:3553'>至於八月有凶消不乆也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3553:3568'>大觀在上順而巽中正以觀天下</span>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3568:3594'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-9a' );" name="003-9a" class="pb">[003-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3594:3617'>　觀字説見彖詞　觀天下之下郭京曰脱是以亨三</span>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3617:3621'>　字</span>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3621:3637'>觀盥而不薦有孚顒若下觀而化也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3637:3660'>　觀而不薦説見彖詞<span class='krp-note'>惠棟作觀盥/而不觀薦</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3660:3683'>觀天之神道而四時不忒聖人以神道設教而天下服</span>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3683:3686'>矣</span>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3686:3719'>　毛竒齡曰王弼以觀字句<span class='krp-note'>查慎行曰觀字自為句/不當連天之神道讀</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3719:3753'>　陸徳明作聖人神道設教無以字<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰古本無/以字  吕祖謙曰</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3753:3779'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-9b' );" name="003-9b" class="pb">[003-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3779:3811'>　<span class='krp-note'>今本有以字字/  惠棟去以</span>　陸時位曰此節古本在文言中後</span>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3811:3820'>　人誤入彖𫝊</span>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3820:3829'>頤中有物曰噬嗑</span>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3829:3852'>噬嗑而亨剛柔分動而明雷電合而章柔得中而上行</span>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3852:3862'>雖不當位利用獄也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3862:3893'>　王弼讀剛柔分動而明<span class='krp-note'>句毛竒齡/  曰大謬</span>　孔頴逹剛柔分</span>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3893:3900'>　<span class='krp-note'>句/</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3900:3904'>賁亨</span>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3904:3931'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-10a' );" name="003-10a" class="pb">[003-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3931:3960'>　朱子曰亨字疑衍<span class='krp-note'>吳澄删/去亨字</span>　陸時位曰亨不是衍字</span>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3960:3974'>　合下故小利有攸往為一節</span>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3974:3998'>柔來而文剛故亨分剛上而文柔故小利有攸往天文也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3998:4021'>　馬椅作柔來而文剛故亨小分剛上而文柔故利有</span>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='4021:4052'>　攸徃　郭京曰天文上脱剛柔交錯一句<span class='krp-note'>徐氏説同/  王昭素</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='4052:4095'>　<span class='krp-note'>胡瑗朱子從之錯石介程子諸儒俱不從入張/振淵曰剛柔交  即在上文㸔出不必添</span>吳澄</span>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='4095:4134'>　增剛柔交錯四字<span class='krp-note'>云王弼注天文也三字自為一節/不與上文連而注云剛柔交錯而</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='4134:4171'>　<span class='krp-note'>成天文則疑若當時此四字未/遺脱然今從胡氏説則補之</span>陸時位于天文也上</span>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='4171:4198'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-10b' );" name="003-10b" class="pb">[003-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='4198:4221'>　加四□□□□以化成天下合為一節云在文言中</span>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='4221:4260'>　後人附入彖傳<span class='krp-note'>云古本天文也上加四口想脱四字/先儒以剛柔交錯代之理亦近是</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='4260:4269'>文明以止人文也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='4269:4288'>觀乎天文以察時變觀乎人文以成化天下</span>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='4288:4297'>剥剥也柔變剛也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='4297:4318'>　京房作剥落也<span class='krp-note'>云脱落字繆/毛竒齡云</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4318:4341'>不利有攸徃小人長也順而止之觀象也君子尚消息</span>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4341:4348'>盈虚天行也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4348:4375'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-11a' );" name="003-11a" class="pb">[003-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4375:4404'>　趙汝楳曰陸徳明作順而止无之字<span class='krp-note'>廉按陸氏釋/文有之字</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4404:4427'>　陸時位以順而止四句别為一節云古本在文言下</span>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4427:4436'>　後人附入彖傳</span>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4436:4442'>復亨剛反</span>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4442:4459'>動而以順行是以出入无疾朋來无咎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4459:4489'>　虞翻王弼孔頴逹讀剛反動而以順行<span class='krp-note'>句惠棟毛/  竒齡同</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4489:4519'>　陸德明曰剛反絶句<span class='krp-note'>程子朱子/諸儒從之</span>　郭京曰剛反下有</span>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4519:4555'>　也字吳澄增也字朱升同<span class='krp-note'>毛竒齡曰剛反動而連下/至順行七字漢魏讀皆如</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4555:4582'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-11b' );" name="003-11b" class="pb">[003-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4582:4624'>　<span class='krp-note'>此後儒以此作句本屬杜撰而朱升旁注竟増/也字彼亦以世無剛反句也然增字則益妄矣</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4624:4637'>反復其道七日來復天行也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4637:4646'>利有攸徃剛長也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4646:4656'>復其見天地之心乎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4656:4679'>无妄剛自外來而為主于内動而健剛中而應大亨以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4679:4702'>正天之命也其匪正有眚不利有攸徃无妄之徃何之</span>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4702:4712'>矣天命不佑行矣哉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4712:4740'>　郭京作動而愈健<span class='krp-note'>云脱/愈字</span>　佑馬融作右謂天不右行</span>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4740:4767'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-12a' );" name="003-12a" class="pb">[003-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4767:4808'>　<span class='krp-note'>李鼎祚作右引虞翻曰右助也馬君非/云天命不右行非矣  晁説之曰馬</span>　陸徳明曰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4808:4826'>　本又作祐<span class='krp-note'>吕祖謙曰/今本作祐</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4826:4840'>大畜剛健篤實輝光日新其徳</span>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4840:4870'>　鄭𤣥虞翻管輅篤實<span class='krp-note'>句/</span>輝光日新<span class='krp-note'>句/</span>其徳剛上而尚</span>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4870:4912'>　賢<span class='krp-note'>句崔憬新俗李鼎祚惠棟同/  云日    讀属下失之</span>陸徳明大畜剛健<span class='krp-note'>句/</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4912:4944'>　篤寔輝光<span class='krp-note'>句/</span>日新其徳<span class='krp-note'>句/</span>王弼諸儒以剛健篤寔<span class='krp-note'>句/</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4944:4986'>　輝光日新其徳<span class='krp-note'>句毛竒齡曰鄭𤣥諸儒皆以篤實句/  輝光日新句李氏集解亦以此章</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4986:5024'>　<span class='krp-note'>惟王弼本以其徳章/句而宋人宗之非是</span>　輝陸徳明李鼎祚作煇<span class='krp-note'>惠棟/同</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='5024:5051'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-12b' );" name="003-12b" class="pb">[003-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='5051:5064'>剛上而尚賢能止健大正也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='5064:5104'>　能止健虞翻作健止<span class='krp-note'>云舊讀能止健誤也云李鼎祚/同  惠棟作能健止  舊讀不</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='5104:5114'>　<span class='krp-note'>合彖/傳例</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='5114:5123'>不家食吉養賢也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='5123:5133'>利渉大川應乎天也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='5133:5156'>頤貞吉養正則吉也觀頤觀其所養也自求口實觀其</span>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='5156:5161'>自養也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='5161:5182'>天地養萬物聖人養賢以及萬民頤之時大矣哉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='5182:5209'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-13a' );" name="003-13a" class="pb">[003-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='5209:5217'>大過大者過也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='5217:5225'>棟橈本末弱也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='5225:5249'>　弱陸徳明曰本亦作溺<span class='krp-note'>晁說之曰溺/古文弱字</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='5249:5258'>大過之時大矣哉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='5258:5265'>習坎重險也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='5265:5279'>水流而不盈行險而不失其信</span>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='5279:5296'>維心亨乃以剛中也行有尚徃有功也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5296:5319'>天險不可升也地險山川丘陵也王公設險以守其國</span>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5319:5346'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-13b' );" name="003-13b" class="pb">[003-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5346:5355'>險之時用大矣哉</span>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5355:5394'>　國虞翻李鼎祚作邦<span class='krp-note'>惠棟同避云舊作國尋邦與升/陵韻漢  諱改為國虞氏本正</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5394:5403'>　<span class='krp-note'>作邦/也</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5403:5426'>離麗也日月麗乎天百榖草木麗乎土重明以麗乎正</span>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5426:5433'>乃化成天下</span>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5433:5471'>　麗乎土許慎作䕻於地<span class='krp-note'>顧野王引作䕻乎地云䕻附/著也本亦作麗  晁説之曰</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5471:5508'>　<span class='krp-note'>麗篆文䕻/别篆文</span>　土虞翻王肅李鼎祚作地<span class='krp-note'>晁說之曰一/行作地惠棟</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5508:5539'>　<span class='krp-note'>同/</span>　陸時位以柔麗乎中正三句屬離麗也下<span class='krp-note'>云照/古本</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5539:5566'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '003-14a' );" name="003-14a" class="pb">[003-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5566:5613'>　<span class='krp-note'>今本改竄失其義矣乎毛竒齡曰張氏玩辭以離麗/也三句後接日月麗  天四句似較諸卦辭例相合</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5613:5623'>　<span class='krp-note'>當備/參考</span></span>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5623:5639'>柔麗乎中正故亨是以畜牝牛吉也</span>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5639:5642'>　</span>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5642:5645'>　</span>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5645:5648'>　</span>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5648:5651'>　</span>
